description:
Mao is another esper with telekinetic powers from the same organization as http://anidb.net/ch93274 [Hina] and http://anidb.net/ch93272 [Anzu]. After being sent to recover them both, she accidentally lands on a deserted island and is stuck there for months without human contact, creating wooden puppet versions of Hina and Anzu to keep from going insane.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Mao
